rbm-deb-src(1)
==============

NAME
----
rbm-deb-src - Create debian source package


SYNOPSIS
--------
[verse]
'rbm deb-src' <project> [options]

DESCRIPTION
-----------

Create a debian source package for the selected project.

This is equivalent to running 'rbm build --step deb_src <project>'.

